- make sure prev isValid (if already validated)
Weird stuff. index to block index, but not in active chain
-- check if block matches checkpoint block(up to this pt)
- verify there was no fork prior checkpoint -- or throw
- check txs are sorted with CTOR - if magneticAnomaly
- bip34 deployment and coinbase height check
@call DisconnectTip -- if there are invalidate blocks
@call ConnectTip (for all blocks that are pending, reorgs)
- is block after current tip ? (SAME Chain?)
- if no block, read from disk
- if bip30 -> for each tx in block verify dup tx in UTXO.
- nLockTimeFlags |= verify sequence if CSV activated
- nSigopCount - recalculate sigops because of P2SH
- check sequence locks - throw non final
- checksig check queue - add tx sig checks
- blockReward - check coinbase spending correct amount
- clear mempool if replay protection is enabled
- if we have non mandatory flag -- Check scriptSig
